<p><strong>Cost.</strong> AI tools reduce cost-per-asset by 40-60%. For a business publishing 30 social posts per month, that is a meaningful budget savings.</p>
<p><strong>Scale across platforms.</strong> A single core idea can become a LinkedIn article, an Instagram carousel, an X thread, and a Facebook post. AI handles the reformatting. A human handles the strategy.</p>
